title: Match history not updating, games missing holes here and there...
body:
I have a couple of games not showing up in match history either in client or on the website.
I should have in order of MOST RECENT in match history has it should appear, but ones that are ~~stroked out~~ are missing:
{{champion:16}}  WIN Normal
{{champion:16}}  LOSS Normal
{{champion:15}}  WIN Normal
{{champion:15}}  ~~LOSS Normal~~
{{champion:16}}  ~~WIN Coop vs AI ~~
{{champion:15}}  ~~WIN ranked~~
{{champion:15}}  WIN ranked
{{champion:15}}  WIN ranked

After the third Ranked Sivir game was missing both in client and on web I played a quick Coop vs AI game to try to see if it would fix it, and that game is missing too. Games have been appearing after that.

[Here is my match history on web](http://matchhistory.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-history/NA1/205476698)

[Here is an image of my game recorder and client game history, I don't record Co-op vs AI games](http://i63.tinypic.com/lbe41.jpg)

replies.body: i've been having the same issue, also had a win in match history for a ranked but showed as a lose in my win/lose record
